examples.en: They examine their products for defects.
The drug was found to cause serious birth defects.
The products showed a remarkable absence of defects.
Vanity and pride were his two worst character defects.
This device permits detection of defects in the lungs.
The washer comes with a guarantee against major defects.
These stockings are seconds and have some slight defects.
Close inspection of the candles revealed some small defects.
All the cars are tested for defects before they leave the factory.
If there are any defects you should send it back to the manufacturer.
The parents are seeking compensation for birth defects caused by the drug.
